OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FVeteran politician Ann Widdecombe was
OL,7,Fkilled in a "targeted attack", counter-
OL,8,Fterrorism police investigating her
OL,9,Fdeath have said.
OL,11,FFormer MEP Miss Widdecombe, 78, was
OL,12,Ffound dead at her home in Haytor on
OL,13,FDartmoor, Devon last Thursday.
OL,15,FCounter-terrorism police are now
OL,16,Fleading the investigation into the
OL,17,Fformer Conservative minister's death
OL,18,Fafter new evidence came to light, but
OL,19,Fa senior officer stressed the murder
OL,20,Fand terror investigations are
OL,21,Fcurrently working "in parallel".
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@]O]}D@SOU}D@_O]
