OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FHead of Counter Terrorism Policing,
OL,7,FAssistant Commissioner Laurence Taylor
OL,8,Ftold reporters: "It is clear that this
OL,9,Fwas a targeted attack.
OL,11,F"We are still working to understand
OL,12,Fthe extent of any planning or
OL,13,Fpreparation, and the motivation that
OL,14,Fsits behind that attack.
OL,16,F"I wouldn't want to comment on what
OL,17,Fthat motivation was.
OL,19,F"The two investigations are running in
OL,20,Fparallel," he added.
OL,26,@pD@QOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,F"In terms of the preparation and
OL,7,Fplanning, we are aware that there has
OL,8,Fbeen some preparation and planning. I
OL,9,Fdon't want to go into the details of
OL,10,Fthe extent of that at this stage."
OL,12,FA 28-year-old white British man
OL,13,Fremains under arrest on suspicion of
OL,14,Fcommission, preparation, or
OL,15,Finstigation of acts of terrorism, as
OL,16,Fwell as on suspicion of murder, the
OL,17,FAssistant Commissioner said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
