CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FOfficer have been granted a warrant of
OL,7,Ffurther detention meaning the suspect
OL,8,Fcan now be held for questioning for up
OL,9,Fto seven days under the Terrorism Act,
OL,10,Fhe added.
OL,12,F"There are multiple lines of inquiry
OL,13,Fthat we are pursuing expeditiously,
OL,14,Fand that includes a number of digital
OL,15,Fforensic examinations," the senior
OL,16,Fofficer continued.
OL,18,F"It is important to remember that this
OL,19,Fis a murder investigation following a
OL,20,Fbrutal attack on a 78-year-old lady in
OL,21,Fher home."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@WO]zD@AOU}D@JO]
