OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FMiss Widdecombe's body was discovered
OL,7,Fat about 11.40am on Thursday at her
OL,8,Fremote bungalow. She had sustained
OL,9,Fserious injuries.
OL,11,FPolice said looking at whether the
OL,12,Fsuspect in the alleged murder of Ann
OL,13,FWiddecombe was targeting Reform UK
OL,14,Ffigures will be a "line of inquiry".
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
