OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FAsked by reporters whether the police
OL,7,Finvestigation was looking at whether
OL,8,Fthe suspect was targeting "other
OL,9,FReform politicians", Assistant
OL,10,FCommissioner Laurence Taylor said: "So
OL,11,Fclearly, part of our responsibility
OL,12,Fwhen investigating offences of this
OL,13,Fnature is to assure ourselves and
OL,14,Ftherefore the public and others of any
OL,15,Fextant of threat.
OL,17,F"That will form a line of
OL,18,Finvestigation to ensure that we are
OL,19,Fputting all appropriate measures in
OL,20,Fplace to mitigate any threat, should
OL,21,Fit become apparent.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@SO]rD@dOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
