OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,F"I'm not saying there is or there
OL,7,Fisn't at this stage."
OL,9,FHe added: "Of course that will be a
OL,10,Fline of inquiry."
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood told
OL,13,Fthe House of Commons on Monday the
OL,14,Fsuspect was not known to the
OL,15,FGovernment anti-extremism scheme
OL,16,FPrevent.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@UO]qD@KOUrD@QO]
