OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FFootage was shared with media outlets,
OL,7,Fincluding the Sun newspaper and Sky
OL,8,FNews, showing a man with no top on
OL,9,Fbeing arrested and led away from a
OL,10,Fhouse in Rotherham, South Yorkshire,
OL,11,Fon Saturday.
OL,13,FPolice believe Miss Widdecombe was
OL,14,Fattacked on Wednesday at about
OL,15,F12.30pm, shortly before she had been
OL,16,Fdue on Channel 5's Matt Allwright show.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
