OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784184477
OL,3,CAnn Widdecombe killed in 'targeted
OL,4,Cattack', say counter-terrorism police
OL,6,FITV News later published a series of
OL,7,FWhatsApp images that appear to show
OL,8,Fthat Miss Widdecombe stopped
OL,9,Fresponding to messages from a TV
OL,10,Fproducer after the approximate time
OL,11,Fpolice believe the attack took place
OL,12,Fthat day.
OL,14,FMiss Widdecombe was first elected a
OL,15,FConservative MP in Kent in 1987, and
OL,16,Fwent on to become an MEP for the
OL,17,FBrexit Party and then a spokeswoman
OL,18,Ffor Reform UK.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
